text:
e="preserve">Lucie Nová (born 1 April 1991) is a Czech volleyball player.
She played at the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, and 2017–18 CEV Women's Champions League.
She played for PVK Olymp Praha and VK Prostějov.
